    "body": "Currently we have a function `cudf.isclose` that is undocumented. It mirrors `cupy.isclose` but also has null support. Pandas does not have a similar `isclose` function. After discussion with @shwina, @galipremsagar, and @vyasr we decided to deprecate and remove this function.\r\n\r\nSee also: https://github.com/rapidsai/cudf/issues/5105\r\n\r\nAs part of the deprecation, we decided to add a warning message indicating how to support nulls while using `cupy.isclose`.",
